00:30:14,025 --> 00:30:16,727
[SPEAKER_00]: Hi, I'm Officer Patrick Smith.

548
00:30:17,287 --> 00:30:20,909
[SPEAKER_00]: I've been a police officer over 10 years, born and raised in Medford.

549
00:30:22,130 --> 00:30:23,411
[SPEAKER_00]: My father was a police officer.

550
00:30:23,852 --> 00:30:26,774
[SPEAKER_00]: I did the underage buys when I was a teenager.

551
00:30:28,043 --> 00:30:30,964
[SPEAKER_00]: And before I was, I joined the Medford police in 2016.

552
00:30:31,444 --> 00:30:33,624
[SPEAKER_00]: Before that I was a police officer in the town of Saltboro.

553
00:30:34,344 --> 00:30:40,585
