573
00:31:49,060 --> 00:32:08,647
[SPEAKER_11]: I make a motion to accept Officer Smith and Officer Sebastian as agents of the Liquor Board, and they will report to Officer Lockowitz, and Officer Lockowitz will help us through the hard times and the good times.

